{"tid":957174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港女係由細培養而成","createTime":"2018-12-26T22:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T13:59:05.000Z","uid":201091,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26dac56d249791578a371622675dcf51015a222b","tid":957174,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T22:35:34.000Z","msg":"話説琴日搭巴士個陣<br />\n我前面排住個細路女<br />\n咁上車個陣<br />\n佢唔係拎張八達通出黎嘟<br />\n而係成個手袋拍落去<br />\n八達通感應唔到啦<br />\n佢仲唔拎張八達通出黎<br />\n係到磨磨磨<br />\n搞咗成三十秒先上到車<br />\n咁細個已經係咁<br />\n大個一定係港女<br />\n所以話港女係由細培養而成"},{"pid":"b0e8702d143613a4a99a790791dfd9d90c7ba1b9","tid":957174,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T22:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ed485d0bf2b9e173f56621559e23abdecdd465","tid":957174,"uid":37537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T22:42:45.000Z","msg":"佢老母都應該係呢啲西港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5af2448e83052f406f2beeb2f82d19981d3eeb","tid":957174,"uid":201091,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"55ed485d0bf2b9e173f56621559e23abdecdd465","tid":957174,"uid":37537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T22:42:45.000Z","msg":"佢老母都應該係呢啲西港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T22:44:47.000Z","msg":"家教好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710f011494f985c9ce0ef3b8fd4c35afd70af2b7","tid":957174,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T22:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3c0427f028edfbc0453f3d7c3ad5acfb83f3ad","tid":957174,"uid":201091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T23:05:44.000Z","msg":"死港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653ff01a2ed64b7e1dd4ccf824